ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Recommended for those with specialized interest in related fields only.

This was a focused look at a specific topic in Stoic logic, i.e., Stoic speech act. I would recommend it to any other student interested in ancient philosophy or contemporary logic, philosophy of language.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course definitely deepened my knowledge of Stoic speech act and raised interesting questions for future research. It did not contribute to my dissertation research.
